></div><span class="Text Text__body3"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2689556698">Edited <!-- -->January 22, 2021</a></span></section><section class="ReviewText"><section class="ReviewText__content"><div class="TruncatedText"><div class="TruncatedText__text TruncatedText__text--5" data-testid="contentContainer"><div><span class="Formatted">22/1/21<br>Finally did a full review on this one :)<br><b>------------------<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-M4UlBNL9xc" rel="nofollow noopener">VIDEO REVIEW</a>------------------</b><br><img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1611312223i/30738522._SX540_.png" class="gr-hostedUserImg" loading="lazy"><br><br>3/6/20<br>This was interesting! I do however have to say that I enjoyed No Longer Human far more.<br><br>2/6/20<br>Dazai's novel No Longer Human really struck a cord with me, so I am very excited to give this one a go today!<br><br>20/3/19<br>I will be reading this book in the coming weeks for my Around the World in Books Series on Youtube.<br><br>You can find me on<br><a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCamkpihJtPvMuH49D6FejEw" rel="nofollow noopener">Youtube</a> | <a href="https://www.instagram.com/theartisangeek/" rel="nofollow noopener">Instagram</a> | <a href="https://www.twitch.tv/theartisangeek" rel="nofollow noopener">Twitch</a> | <a href="https://twitter.com/TheArtisanGeek" rel="nofollow noopener">Twitter</a> | <a href="http://theartisangeek.tumblr.com/" rel="nofollow noopener">Tumblr</a> | <a href="https://theartisangeek.com/" rel="nofollow noopener">Website</a> | <a href="https://thestorygraph.com/index.html" rel="nofollow noopener">The Storygraph</a></span></div></div></div></section></section><section class="ReviewCard__tags"><ul class="CollapsableList"></ul></section><footer class="SocialFooter"><div data-testid="stats" class="SocialFooter__statsContainer"><div class="Button__container"><button type="button" class="Button Button--inline B